      <br/>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <p>
       Research in DOLCIT is unique, in part, because of its focus on the interplay between the application domains and analytic tools above. This shows up in many of the
       <a href="research.html">
        ongoing projects
       </a>
       in the group as well as in the broad backgrounds of the
       <a href="people.html">
        faculty and students
       </a>
       that make up DOLCIT.
       <br/>
       <br/>
       <strong>
        Interested in joining DOLCIT?
       </strong>
       We are actively recruiting students and postdocs.
       <a href="joinus.html">
        Click here for more information.
       </a>
      </p>
